<div class="row w-100 m-0" style="overflow: hidden">
	<div id="section-main" class="sermons-col-left bg-grey" style="width:100%">
		<h1 class="color-1a8090 bg-white text-center pb-2 pt-3 h2">第85屆 奮興會 第9講</h1>
		<article class="article pt-0 p-lg-5 pt-lg-0">
			<div class="article-meta">
				<span>
					<i class="fa fa-user"></i>
					講員：					<a href="/speaker/view/37">費蘭度博士</a>
				</span>
				<span>
					<i class="fa fa-calendar-alt"></i>
					屆別:					<a href="/sermon/view?serial_no=85">第85屆</a>
				</span>
				<span data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top" title="性質">
					<i class="fa fa-folder-open"></i>
					<a href="/sermon/view?serial_no=85#session-master-49">奮興會</a>
				</span>
			</div>
			<!--<div class="article-tag">
				<a href="#" class="badge">路加福音</a>
				<a href="#" class="badge">講道會</a>
				<a href="#" class="badge">56屆</a>
				<a href="#" class="badge">麥希真牧師</a>
			</div>-->
			<div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-4">
				<h2 class="article-title mb-0 h3">
					第九講  忿怒 — 道德之人的缺點				</h2>
									<a type="button" class="bookmark ms-3 " data-model="app\models\SessionMessage" data-model-id="854"></a>
							</div>
						<div class="article-content">
				
				<div class="h5 mb-4 d-md-flex justify-content-lg-between align-items-center">
					<div><span>經文：</span> 哥林多前書  <a class="article-citation" href="javascript:void(0)" data-book="46" data-start-chapter="13" data-start-verse="5">13:5</a></div><div><a href="javascript:void(0)" class="btn btn-danger btn-show-scripture text-center my-2 ml-auto align-self-start" style="display:none;">顯示經文</a>
				</div></div>				<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">今晚我們將會提到「怒氣」。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">傳教士</span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">Henry有一本著作《世間最重要的事》。這本書中提及怒氣是道德之人的缺點。他表明如果人容易發怒的話，其個性也必定充滿缺點。Henry說:「怒氣是錯誤的，我們要麼嚴肅地把怒氣當作一回事。」聖經中一再提及，怒氣是摧毀人的個性，及帶來不幸的元兇。在哥林多前書13:5，保羅表示:「愛是不輕易發怒。」</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">保羅提及不輕易發怒的意思，是指日常中不必要的情緒。這也是基督徒常犯的錯誤，若常發怒，怎能去傳福音呢？</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">我事奉機構的接任人也叫費蘭度，不過姓氏不同。有天晚上，他們聚會時，有個歹徒威嚇要燒掉房屋。接任人和太太很害怕，但仍然堅持留守。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">第二天早上，接任人竟然上門找那個歹徒，歹徒出來說</span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">:「看到你真得太好了。」為什麼昨天這麼惡，今天卻改變了態度？歹徒說:「你知道嗎？昨晚我們惡言恐嚇，但你竟然微笑相對，我回家想到你的微笑，整夜睡不著。」結果，兩人成了好朋友。這不是一個很好的見證嗎？</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">有位</span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">Mary希望丈夫能信主，她丈夫說:「要是基督徒都像你這樣壞脾氣，我才不要相信主。」牧師就告訴Mary不要再發怒，要祈求神把脾氣變好。於是，Mary祈禱:「主啊，我重新把自己交託給你，求祢賜我力量，讓我不再發怒。」</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">過了不久，</span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">Mary丈夫裝修房子打破了一個新花瓶，他知道情況不妙了，但Mary卻不生氣，丈夫感到奇怪。Mary回答:「親愛的，主耶穌改變了我的壞脾氣。」丈夫聽後，便說:「如果耶穌能改變你這種人，我也希望得到醫治，讓我們祈禱吧。」丈夫就在此刻信了主。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">人發怒的五個原因：</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">1）漠視後果</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">加拉太書</span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">6:7說，種瓜得瓜，種豆得豆。些人發怒時，說出種下禍根的說話，然後連自己也忘記了，也許曾經後悔過，過後就忘了。但受傷害的人並不忘記，有些傷害是持續的。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">我以前很容易對兄弟和母親發怒，信主後，我會對他們道歉。有時候，我們需要朋友的幫助。但如果你連這樣的朋友也沒有，你就失去了神給你一種的祝福。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">2）由於罪疚</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">詩篇</span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">51:12中，大衛為自己的罪禱告:「求祢使我仍得救恩之樂，賜我樂意的靈扶持我。」當我們對付罪，就能重得喜樂。如果不對付，心中有罪惡感，也容易發怒。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">「神所賜出人意外的平安、必在基督耶穌裡、保守你們的心懷意念。」</span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">(腓4:7)保守的意思，就是防衛你的心態。當我們犯罪時，我們的平安便會失去。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">「又要叫基督的平安在你們心裡作主。你們也為此蒙召、歸為一體，且要存感謝的心。」</span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">(西3:15)如果你心中失去平安，這是非常清楚的訊號，就是你出了毛病。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">3）由於記憶裡的傷痕</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">另一個使人發怒的原因，就是心靈和記憶裡的傷痕未受醫治。哥林多前書</span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">13章曾經提過這點，所以今晚就不多說。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">4）由於特殊的壓力</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">特別的壓力，家庭中的壓力，工作的壓力，或是經濟的壓力</span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">...我們活在多重壓力之下，難怪有很多的怒氣。遇到壓力時，有三個解決方法：</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">&nbsp; &nbsp; 1. 假如發怒了，要立刻道歉</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">道歉，可令事情改變。我在工作中也有很多壓力，因此我告訴孩子</span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">:「萬一我發怒了，這不是你們的錯，那是因為我遇到很多的壓力。」孩子的思想幼稚，若不說明白，就會以為是自己錯了，所以令到父母對峙。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">有時我們會找藉口，令自己不用道歉，但道歉是必須的。人人都會做錯，假如領袖做錯不認錯，就失去別人對他尊重。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">&nbsp; &nbsp; 2.與朋友分擔</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">傳道書說如果有人跌倒了，但沒有朋友扶起他，這是多麼可惜啊。加拉太書</span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">6:2說:「你們各人的重擔要互相擔當。」我們需要朋友來分擔壓力。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 3.花時間與神相交</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">面對巨大的壓力，最重要的就是把壓力和重擔卸給我們的主。彼得前書</span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">5:1說:「你們把一切的重擔卸給神，因為祂顧念你們。」詩篇55:22：「你要把你的重擔卸給耶和華，祂必撫養你。祂永不叫義人動搖。」</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">腓立比書</span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">4:6-7「應當一無挂慮，只要凡事藉著禱告、祈求，和感謝，將你們所要的告訴神。」當把需要告訴神時，會有什麼後果呢？第7章說:「神所賜出人意外的平安、必在基督耶穌裡，保守你們的心懷意念。」</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">我從危機中學到一個原則，就是在發怒前，你應該先與神對話。我們是神的兒女，因為凡事都出於神，所以面對人之前，我們先要面對神。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">5）不夠休息</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">工作壓力大，會使人休息不夠，容易發怒的其中一個原因，就是不夠休息。司布真是偉大的佈道家，但也有情緒低落的時候。在一次的退修會中，他忙到連睡覺的時間都沒有，神亦賜下奇妙能力讓他帶領聚會。但回家後，當孩子哭泣時，他大聲呼喝孩子。經過艱巨工作後，他的神經已很緊張了。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">有時生病後，情緒也會低落，遇到這樣的情況要對症下藥，注意休息，重新調較生活節奏。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">要抑制怒氣，但如何做到呢？「愛是不計較人的惡。」</span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">(林前13:5)「不計較」就是不計算。基督徒面對傷害，不要記下來作計較。因為神在基督裡寬恕了我們，祂不計算我們的罪。同樣，我們也不要計較別人的過錯。我知道，別人傷害我們之後是很難忘記的，但可以把事情放下嗎？事情已成了錯誤，就不要再受到它的折磨。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">保羅列舉了兩個要原諒別人的原因：一是因為神的大愛已降臨在我們身上。二是神能把不幸的事變為好事。這樣我們就不再受傷害了，也不再抱怨了。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">有人說</span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">:「我原諒你了。」雖然口說原諒，但有些傷害是一生之久。那個傷害你人比神更偉大嗎？如果你是神的兒女，沒有人能夠傷害你一生。要是有，傷害你的只是你自己。只要將自己向神開放，神能夠把不好的事變成益處。既然不好的事都變成益處，那麼，你為什麼還要生氣呢？</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
				
				<br>
				<p class="h5">
					<span>講員：</span> 費蘭度博士
					<br>
					<span>速記：</span> 曉明
				</p>			</div>
			<div class="article-navigation d-flex justify-content-between mt-5">
